{"id":10761,"date":"2024-03-17T15:02:56","date_gmt":"2024-03-17T08:02:56","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/?p=10761"},"modified":"2024-03-17T15:27:45","modified_gmt":"2024-03-17T08:27:45","slug":"logia-la-gi","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/logia-la-gi\/","title":{"rendered":"L\u00f4 gia l\u00e0 g\u00ec? L\u00f4 gia kh\u00e1c g\u00ec v\u1edbi ban c\u00f4ng?"},"content":{"rendered":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Logia l\u00e0 m\u1eabu thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u01b0a chu\u1ed9ng khi x\u00e2y nh\u00e0 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn chung c\u01b0. Lo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh logia n\u00e0y v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ti\u1ec7n nghi v\u00e0 kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1eeb ban c\u00f4ng. V\u1eady <\/span><b>logia l\u00e0 g\u00ec? <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/vinhomeland.com.vn\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Vinhomeland<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u chi ti\u1ebft h\u01a1n trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y nh\u00e9!<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>L\u00f4 gia l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Logia l\u00e0 thu\u1eadt ng\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9ng trong ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng, thu\u1eadt ng\u1eef n\u00e0y b\u1eaft ngu\u1ed3n t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1400 TCN trong Hy L\u1ea1p, hi\u1ec7n nay m\u1eabu thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf d\u1ea7n ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u qu\u1ed1c gia nh\u01b0 Anh, M\u1ef9, \u00dd,&#8230; V\u00e0 m\u1ed7i n\u01a1i s\u1ebd mang m\u1ed9t n\u00e9t \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o kh\u00e1c nhau.<\/span><\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_10762\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10762\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10762 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/logia-la-gi-1.jpg\" alt=\"logia l\u00e0 g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/450;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10762\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10762\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/logia-la-gi-1.jpg\" alt=\"logia l\u00e0 g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-10762\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Logia l\u00e0 thu\u1eadt ng\u1eef ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac b\u1eaft ngu\u1ed3n t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1400 TCN trong Hy L\u1ea1p<\/p><\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Logia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n h\u00e0nh lang ngo\u00e0i c\u0103n nh\u00e0, tuy nhi\u00ean n\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e2y th\u1ee5t s\u00e2u v\u00e0o b\u00ean trong v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bao b\u1ecdc b\u1edfi hai b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t ra kh\u1ecfi m\u1eb7t b\u1eb1ng c\u0103n nh\u00e0. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 li\u00ean t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ed9c b\u00e0n, k\u00e9o ra ngo\u00e0i th\u00ec ph\u1ea7n h\u1ecdc b\u00e0n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 ban c\u00f4ng, c\u00f2n thu v\u00e0o th\u00ec ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 logia.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Trong ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac, logia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chia l\u00e0m 2 lo\u1ea1i l\u00e0 logia ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i v\u00e0 logia ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5. Logia ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 n\u01a1i sinh ho\u1ea1t chung n\u00ean s\u1ebd n\u1eb1m c\u1ea1nh nh\u00e0 b\u1ebfp v\u00e0 nh\u00e0 v\u1ec7 sinh, c\u00f2n logia ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i l\u00e0 n\u01a1i \u0111\u1ec3 th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n n\u00ean s\u1ebd g\u1eafn li\u1ec1n v\u1edbi ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Nh\u1eefng quy chu\u1ea9n t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a logia th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Nh\u1eefng c\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh cao t\u1ea7ng, cao c\u1ea5p v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb t\u1ea7ng 6 tr\u1edf \u0111i s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng logia.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Logia kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1edf ph\u1ea7n n\u1ec1n b\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi, chi\u1ec1u cao ph\u1ea3i t\u1eeb 1m2 tr\u1edf l\u00ean.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>\u01afu \u0111i\u1ec3m<\/b><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Logia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e2y th\u1ee5t v\u00e0o b\u00ean trong c\u0103n nh\u00e0 n\u00ean s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu nhi\u1ec1u \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a ngo\u1ea1i c\u1ea3nh nh\u01b0 th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft, kh\u00ed h\u1eadu. Do \u0111\u00f3, logia th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eb7t, ph\u01a1i qu\u1ea7n \u00e1o v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t n\u00f3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ec1n kh\u00e1 cao.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">T\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian sinh ho\u1ea1t t\u00e1ch ri\u00eang v\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng gian b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i, gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ri\u00eang t\u01b0 cho gia ch\u1ee7.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng, logia c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u giao \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb 2 \u0111\u1ebfn 2,4m. Tuy nhi\u00ean, gia ch\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00f9y ch\u1ec9nh k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc sao cho ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhu c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Sau nh\u1eefng b\u1ed9n b\u1ec1 c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c, cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng th\u00ec logia l\u00e0 n\u01a1i l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n, chi\u00eam ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng s\u1eafc m\u00e0u thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean, phong c\u1ea3nh.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">V\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ecbu l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t n\u00ean th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u01b0u gi\u1eef c\u00e1c v\u1eadt d\u1ee5ng, \u0111\u1ed3 ngh\u1ec1 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft cho c\u0103n nh\u00e0.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Gia t\u0103ng th\u00eam ngu\u1ed3n s\u00e1ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, mang \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng, d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.\u00a0\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>Nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m<\/b><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Do \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e2y l\u00f9i v\u00e0o trong v\u1edbi ba m\u1eb7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf k\u00edn n\u00ean s\u1ebd l\u00e0m cho t\u1ea7m nh\u00ecn b\u1ecb h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf.\u00a0\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch sinh ho\u1ea1t b\u1ecb thu gi\u1ea3m, l\u00e0m cho kh\u00f4ng gian b\u1ecb thu h\u1eb9p l\u1ea1i.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>Ban c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi logia, ban c\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e2y nh\u00f4 ra kh\u1ecfi m\u1eb7t b\u1eb1ng nh\u00e0 theo k\u1ebft c\u1ea5u console. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi m\u00e1i che, gia ch\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u t\u00f9y ch\u1ec9nh theo s\u1edf th\u00edch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ban c\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 th\u00edch h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 th\u1ea5p t\u1ea7ng, villa hay bi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 an to\u00e0n.<\/span><\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_10763\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10763\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10763 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/logia-la-gi-2.jpg\" alt=\"logia l\u00e0 g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/450;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10763\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10763\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/logia-la-gi-2.jpg\" alt=\"logia l\u00e0 g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-10763\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ban c\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 th\u1ea5p t\u1ea7ng, villa hay bi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1<\/p><\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Lan can l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec3 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf ban c\u00f4ng. Khi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf lan can, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta th\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng b\u00ea t\u00f4ng, kim lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef cho k\u1ebft c\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc v\u00e0 b\u1ec1n l\u00e2u. D\u00f9 l\u00e0 phong c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i hay t\u00e2n c\u1ed5 \u0111i\u1ec3n th\u00ec lan can \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c m\u1eabu thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u0103n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u0103n nh\u00e0 theo l\u1ed1i t\u00e2n c\u1ed5 \u0111i\u1ec3n th\u00ec ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ebd ch\u1ecdn m\u1eabu u\u1ed1n l\u01b0\u1ee3n, c\u1ea7u k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng th\u00eam s\u1ef1 sang tr\u1ecdng, \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. C\u00f2n nh\u1eefng c\u0103n h\u1ed9 theo h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1ed1i gi\u1ea3n, hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i th\u00ec s\u1ebd d\u00f9ng k\u00ednh c\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ef1c ho\u1eb7c th\u00e9p \u0111\u1ec3 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">T\u1eeb tr\u00ean v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ban c\u00f4ng, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng quan s\u00e1t t\u1eeb 2 &#8211; 3 h\u01b0\u1edbng nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ban c\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 2 m\u1eb7t tho\u00e1ng do b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed n\u1eb1m \u1edf g\u00f3c t\u01b0\u1eddng hay b\u1ecb ch\u1eafn b\u1edfi nh\u00e0 k\u1ebf b\u00ean n\u00ean vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>\u01afu \u0111i\u1ec3m<\/b><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Kh\u00f4ng gian r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i, t\u1ea7m nh\u00ecn tho\u00e1ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng 2 &#8211; 3 g\u00f3c nh\u00ecn.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">D\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ti\u1ebfp thu \u00e1nh n\u1eafng m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3n gi\u00f3, thu\u1eadn ti\u1ec7n cho vi\u1ec7c ph\u01a1i \u0111\u1ed3.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Gia ch\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o m\u1ed9t g\u00f3c \u201cxanh\u201d \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap thanh l\u1ecdc kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed, l\u00e0m \u0111\u1eb9p cho c\u0103n nh\u00e0.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>Nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m<\/b><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">D\u1ec5 b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1edfi th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft, kh\u00ed h\u1eadu do b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t r\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng cao. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u00fd do l\u00e0m suy gi\u1ea3m tu\u1ed5i th\u1ecd c\u1ee7a ban c\u00f4ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">\u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u00ednh th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho ban c\u00f4ng, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n b\u1ea3o d\u01b0\u1ee1ng v\u00e0 tu s\u1eeda th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>Ph\u00e2n lo\u1ea1i logia<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">\u0110\u1ec3 c\u0103n h\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n tr\u1edf n\u00ean th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 v\u00e0 logic th\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u00ean b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn lo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh logia ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng gian c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u00f3 hai lo\u1ea1i logia ch\u00ednh l\u00e0: logia ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i v\u00e0 logia ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5.<\/span><\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Logia ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i: Th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 n\u01a1i \u0111\u1ec3 gia ch\u1ee7 th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n, do \u0111\u00f3 n\u00f3 s\u1ebd g\u1eafn li\u1ec1n v\u1edbi ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7, ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch ho\u1eb7c l\u00e0 n\u01a1i sinh ho\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a gia \u0111\u00ecnh. Ngo\u00e0i ra, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 trang tr\u00ed canh c\u1ea3nh, hoa l\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o kh\u00f4ng gian \u201cxanh\u201d cho c\u0103n h\u1ed9 ho\u1eb7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 nh\u1ecf.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Logia ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5: Lo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf g\u1ea7n k\u1ec1 v\u1edbi nh\u00e0 b\u1ebfp ho\u1eb7c nh\u00e0 v\u1ec7 sinh. V\u1edbi c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i t\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ef1ng chi\u1ebfm nhi\u1ec1u di\u1ec7n t\u00edch trong nh\u00e0, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng logia \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u01a1i ch\u1ee9a. Ngo\u00e0i ra, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb7t m\u00e1y gi\u1eb7t v\u00e0 ph\u01a1i qu\u1ea7n \u00e1o t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div id=\"attachment_10764\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10764\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10764 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/logia-la-gi-3.jpg\" alt=\"logia l\u00e0 g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/450;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10764\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10764\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/logia-la-gi-3.jpg\" alt=\"logia l\u00e0 g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-10764\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u00f3 hai lo\u1ea1i logia ch\u00ednh l\u00e0: logia ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i v\u00e0 logia ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5<\/p><\/div>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>S\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c nhau gi\u1eefa logia v\u00e0 ban c\u00f4ng<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>Gi\u1ed1ng nhau<\/b><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">C\u1ea3 logia v\u00e0 ban c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n b\u1ed5 tr\u1ee3 trong ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac c\u0103n nh\u00e0, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 cho nhu c\u1ea7u sinh ho\u1ea1t v\u00e0 th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u t\u1ea1o ra c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u00ednh ch\u1ed1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 ch\u1ecbu l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u00f3 th\u00eam lan can \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf nh\u1eefng r\u1ee7i ro nguy hi\u1ec3m.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>Kh\u00e1c nhau<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Tuy c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec3m chung v\u1ec1 m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u01b0ng logia v\u00e0 ban c\u00f4ng l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 ki\u1ec3u thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf ri\u00eang bi\u1ec7t, c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 nh\u01b0:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">T\u1ea7m nh\u00ecn t\u1ea1i logia s\u1ebd b\u1ecb h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf h\u01a1n ban c\u00f4ng &#8211; khu v\u1ef1c c\u00f3 t\u1ea7m 2 &#8211; 3 g\u00f3c nh\u00ecn r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i, tho\u00e1ng m\u00e1t.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">M\u00e1i che c\u1ee7a logia l\u00e0 s\u00e0n c\u1ee7a c\u0103n h\u1ed9 tr\u00ean c\u00f2n m\u00e1i che c\u1ee7a ban c\u00f4ng c\u00f3 hay kh\u00f4ng t\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o nhu c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a gia ch\u1ee7.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Logia s\u1edf h\u1eefu k\u1ebft c\u1ea5u m\u1eb7t s\u00e0n c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n nh\u01b0 s\u00e0n nh\u00e0, c\u00f2n s\u00e0n ban c\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf theo ki\u1ec3u console.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Logia c\u00f3 k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc dao \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb 2 &#8211; 2,4m, c\u00f2n ban c\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 t\u1eeb 1 &#8211; 1,5m.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 s\u1ebd thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logia t\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng c\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh cao t\u1ea7ng, c\u00f2n ban c\u00f4ng th\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e2y \u1edf c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 th\u1ea5p t\u1ea7ng, villa hay bi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>C\u00e1c quy \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logia<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Nh\u1eefng c\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1eaft tay v\u00e0o th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00ec c\u1ea7n tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7 theo c\u00e1c quy \u0111\u1ecbnh ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ban h\u00e0nh b\u1edfi B\u1ed9 X\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng. Ri\u00eang logia, ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 c\u1ea7n l\u01b0u \u00fd v\u1edbi c\u00e1c quy \u0111\u1ecbnh sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Nh\u00e0, chung c\u01b0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logia t\u1eeb t\u1ea7ng 6 tr\u1edf l\u00ean, ban c\u00f4ng n\u1eb1m trong v\u00f9ng tr\u00e1i ph\u00e9p.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Lan can thu\u1ed9c logia c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u cao \u00edt nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 1m2, kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea7n ch\u00e2n d\u01b0\u1edbi. V\u1eadt li\u1ec7u x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng lan can c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ec1n cao, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap ch\u1ed1ng ch\u00e1y n\u1ed5 ho\u1eb7c r\u1ee7i ro trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u1ea9n c\u1ea5p. Khuy\u1ebfn kh\u00edch n\u1ebfn l\u1eafp v\u1eadt c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh thay v\u00ec k\u00ednh c\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ef1c tr\u00ean lan can \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ed9 an to\u00e0n.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div id=\"attachment_10765\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10765\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10765 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/logia-la-gi-4.jpg\" alt=\"logia l\u00e0 g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/450;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10765\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10765\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/logia-la-gi-4.jpg\" alt=\"logia l\u00e0 g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-10765\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u00e1c c\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh khi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u1ea7n tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7 theo c\u00e1c quy \u0111\u1ecbnh ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng<\/p><\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, c\u00e1c h\u1ed9 gia \u0111\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n l\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t th\u00eam c\u1eeda s\u1ed5 c\u00f3 l\u1ed7 m\u1edf th\u00f4ng th\u1ee7y v\u1edbi k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 600mm x 600mm \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee9u h\u1ed9 n\u1ebfu x\u1ea3y ra tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p b\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 kh\u00e1ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">K\u1ebft c\u1ea5u logia c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u m\u1eb7t s\u00e0n c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ecbu l\u1ef1c, ch\u1ed1ng th\u1ea5m t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 \u0111a c\u00f4ng n\u0103ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">V\u1eadt li\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o c\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7t t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed khoa h\u1ecdc, logic, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng c\u00e1c v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u th\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng nh\u01b0 than x\u1ec9, b\u00ea t\u00f4ng b\u1ecdt,&#8230;<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Tr\u00e1nh tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p x\u00e2y s\u00e0n nh\u00e0 b\u1ea5p b\u00eanh, ki\u1ec3u c\u00e1ch r\u01b0\u1eddm r\u00e0, \u1ea9m m\u1ed1c, \u0111\u1ecdng n\u01b0\u1edbc.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 m\u1eabu l\u00f4 gia \u0111\u1eb9p cho c\u0103n h\u1ed9<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logia v\u1edbi ti\u1ec3u c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p<\/b><\/span><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Logia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 n\u01a1i l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n, ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi n\u01a1i n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u01b0ng b\u00e0y c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i c\u00e2y c\u1ea3nh, lo\u00e0i hoa \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o. C\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u m\u1eabu thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf ti\u1ec3u c\u1ea3nh b\u1eaft m\u1eaft, ti\u1ec7n t\u00edch ngay c\u1ea1nh logia, ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n nh\u01b0 c\u00e2y xanh k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u hay nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec3u c\u1ea3nh n\u01b0\u1edbc,&#8230;Tuy nhi\u00ean, ta c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1c c\u00e2y c\u00f3 tr\u1ec5 n\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 v\u1ec1 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i.<\/span><\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_10766\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10766\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10766 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/logia-la-gi-5.jpg\" alt=\"logia l\u00e0 g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/450;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10766\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10766\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/logia-la-gi-5.jpg\" alt=\"logia l\u00e0 g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-10766\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Logia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 n\u01a1i l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n, ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i<\/p><\/div>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logia l\u00e0m n\u01a1i ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i<\/b><\/span><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Logia c\u00f3 \u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng, m\u00e1t m\u1ebb, l\u00e0 n\u01a1i \u0111\u00f3n nhi\u1ec1u \u00e1nh n\u1eafng v\u00e0 gi\u00f3 tr\u1eddi, do v\u1eady n\u00f3 th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 n\u01a1i \u0111\u1ec3 gia ch\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n v\u00e0 ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i. B\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n trang b\u1ecb th\u00eam 1 chi\u1ebfc v\u00f5ng, gh\u1ebf l\u01b0\u1eddi hay b\u1ed9 b\u00e0n gh\u1ebf nh\u1ecf, nhi\u00eau \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh n\u01a1i tr\u00f2 chuy\u1ec7n, t\u00e1n g\u1eabu c\u00f9ng gia \u0111\u00ecnh hay b\u1ea1n b\u00e8 \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u01a1i nh\u00e0.<\/span><\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_10767\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10767\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10767 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/logia-la-gi-6.jpg\" alt=\"logia l\u00e0 g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/450;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10767\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10767\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/logia-la-gi-6.jpg\" alt=\"logia l\u00e0 g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-10767\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Logia c\u00f3 \u01b0u th\u1ebf th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng, m\u00e1t m\u1ebb, l\u00e0 n\u01a1i \u0111\u00f3n nhi\u1ec1u \u00e1nh n\u1eafng v\u00e0 gi\u00f3 tr\u1eddi<\/p><\/div>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logia th\u00e0nh n\u01a1i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c, h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp truy\u1ec1n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng<\/b><\/span><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Kh\u00f4ng gian xung quanh c\u0169ng l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00f4ng \u00edt \u0111\u1ebfn qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp v\u00e0 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c. Do v\u1eady, vi\u1ec7c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logia l\u00e0 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft, khi h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp v\u00e0 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c trong m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian s\u00e1ng s\u1ee7a, tho\u00e1ng m\u00e1t s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n ti\u1ebfp th\u00eam n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n c\u1ea3m h\u01a1n, \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_10768\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10768\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10768 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/logia-la-gi-7.jpg\" alt=\"logia l\u00e0 g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/450;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10768\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10768\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/logia-la-gi-7.jpg\" alt=\"logia l\u00e0 g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-10768\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logia l\u00e0 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 cho vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c<\/p><\/div>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>Logia ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 sinh ho\u1ea1t<\/b><\/span><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Khu v\u1ef1c logia v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111a n\u0103ng, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng c\u00e1c nhu c\u1ea7u v\u1ec1 sinh ho\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a gia \u0111\u00ecnh. Ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i hay sinh ho\u1eb7c, logia c\u00f2n nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 kho c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9a \u0111\u1ef1ng c\u00e1c v\u1eadt d\u1ee5ng \u00edt d\u00f9ng hay l\u00e0 n\u01a1i \u0111\u1ec3 m\u00e1y gi\u1eb7t, ph\u01a1i \u0111\u1ed3.<\/span><\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_10769\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10769\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10769 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/logia-la-gi-8.jpg\" alt=\"logia l\u00e0 g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/450;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10769\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10769\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/logia-la-gi-8.jpg\" alt=\"logia l\u00e0 g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-10769\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Logia v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111a n\u0103ng, ti\u1ec7n l\u1ee3i<\/p><\/div>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>T\u1ed5ng k\u1ebft<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">V\u1eady l\u00e0 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e1i qu\u00e1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1ed9i dung c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n cho c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/logia-la-gi\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><b>logia l\u00e0 g\u00ec<\/b><\/a>? <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u1eafm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng \u01b0u nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn m\u1eabu thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logia ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u0103n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n mong mu\u1ed1n m\u1ed9t logia \u0111\u1ea7y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u00ec h\u00e3y li\u00ean h\u1ec7 ngay cho <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Vinhomeland<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> nh\u00e9.<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"kk-star-ratings kksr-auto kksr-align-right kksr-valign-bottom\"\n    data-payload='{&quot;align&quot;:&quot;right&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;10761&quot;,&quot;slug&quot;:&quot;default&quot;,&quot;valign&quot;:&quot;bottom&quot;,&quot;ignore&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;reference&quot;:&quot;auto&quot;,&quot;class&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;count&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;legendonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;readonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;score&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;starsonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;best&quot;:&quot;5&quot;,&quot;gap&quot;:&quot;4&qu